Dear {!Contact.Name}, <br>
<br>
Carhartt is pleased to announce the introduction of several new Flame-Resistant products.  With flame-resistant clothing safety comes first, but comfort is a very close second so we’re adding three new lightweight pants, a lighter weight coverall, and a short sleeve T-shirt. We’re also pleased to announce our innovative new Flame-Resistant Lanyard-Access Jacket that’s specially designed for fall protection. It’s packed with features to include a flapped opening in the back of the jacket which provides a pass-through for a safety harness D-ring, and sleeves that cinch tight for a better fit under long gloves. Finally, for those customers who don’t require the extreme warmth of our existing outerwear, we’re rounding out our line by adding a mid-weight Active Jacket and a new All Seasons Bomber Jacket.    <br>
<br>
Attached you’ll find a brochure highlighting the features of our new Flame-Resistant products. Several of the new products, as pointed out in the brochure, are available to ship today, while the others will be available in January.  <br>
<br>
If you have any questions about any of these products or would like to set-up an appointment to review the line please don’t hesitate to contact me.  My e-mail and phone number are listed below.  <br>
<br>
Thank You for your continued support of the Carhartt Brand. <br>
<br>
Sincerely, <br>
<br>
{!Contact.OwnerFullName} <br>
{!Contact.OwnerPhone} <br>
{!Contact.OwnerEmail} <br>
